import React from "react"; import "../../styles/index.css"; const MissionList = (props) => { const deleteMision = (event) => { props.deleteHandler(event.target.id) } return (
    {props.missionList.map((mission, index) => (

  • Type : {mission.missionType.name}

    Qty : {mission.quantity}

    VINs : {mission.vins}

); }; export default MissionList;
